---
title: Beefy Fusilli Rustica with Zucchini and Toasted Almonds
description: The week just isn’t complete without at least one pasta night. If you agree, you’re in luck! In this recipe, you’ll find fusilli studded with tender zucchini and swirls of sun-dried tomato pesto. The dreamy dish is finished off with a sprinkle of Parmesan and your new secret culinary weapon: toasted almonds!
